#: cards:1
msgid ""
"<p><big>Applicant</big></p>\n"
"\n"
"<ul>\n"
"\t<li>The person selected here will replace the <strong>Applicant</strong>&nbsp;on the <strong>Application Details</strong> step</li>\n"
"\t<li>This field is <strong>required</strong></li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"\n"
"<p><big>Former Licensee</big></p>\n"
"\n"
"<ul>\n"
"\t<li>The people selected in this drop down must exist on the <strong>Application Details</strong> step as a <strong>Nominated Excavation Director(s)</strong></li>\n"
"\t<li>The people selected here will be removed from the <strong>Nominated Excavation Director(s)</strong> on the <strong>Application Details</strong> step</li>\n"
"\t<li>This field is <strong>required</strong></li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"\n"
"<p><big>Nominated Excavation Director</big></p>\n"
"\n"
"<ul>\n"
"\t<li>The people selected here will be put into the <strong>Nominated Excavation Director(s)</strong> field on&nbsp;the <strong>Application Details</strong> step</li>\n"
"\t<li>The people provided here must not already exist in the <strong>Nominated Excavation Director(s)</strong> field&nbsp;on&nbsp;the <strong>Application Details</strong> step</li>\n"
"\t<li>This field is <strong>required</strong></li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"\n"
"<p><big>Former Employing Body &nbsp;</big></p>\n"
"\n"
"<ul>\n"
"\t<li>This field is used to remove an <strong>Employing Body</strong> from the field on the <strong>Application Details</strong> page</li>\n"
"\t<li>The selected <strong>Organisation</strong> must exist in the <strong>Employing Body</strong> field on the&nbsp;on the <strong>Application Details</strong> page</li>\n"
"\t<li>This field is not <strong>required</strong></li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"\n"
"<p><big>Employing Body</big></p>\n"
"\n"
"<ul>\n"
"\t<li>This field is used to add an <strong>Employing Body</strong> to the field on the <strong>Application Details</strong> page</li>\n"
"\t<li>If this field is used without the use of the <strong>Former Employing Body</strong> field. The selected <strong>Employing Body</strong> in this field will be added to the <strong>Employing Body</strong> field on the <strong>Application Details</strong> page</li>\n"
"\t<li>This field is <strong>not required</strong></li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"\n"
"<p><big>Cur Grade E Decision, Made By (Cur Grade E), Cur Grade D Decision and Made By (Cur Grade D)</big></p>\n"
"\n"
"<ul>\n"
"\t<li>These fields are <strong>not required</strong></li>\n"
"\t<li>These fields determine if the transfer will be <strong>applied</strong> to the field on the <strong>Application Details</strong> page or <strong>closed&nbsp;and not appiled</strong></li>\n"
"\t<li>To apply a <strong>Transfer of License</strong> and see it reflected on the <strong>Application Details</strong> page. These fields <strong>are required</strong> and of course must be the positive approval options for the <strong>Decision</strong> fields</li>\n"
"\t<li>One negative approval of the two decision options will mark this as <strong>closed</strong>. If there was also a <strong>Cur Grade D Person</strong> and <strong>Cur Grade E Person</strong> selected</li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
msgstr ""

